%% to download measurements from spectraScan650%% These are the measures where I check the push-pull MT experiment.%% cmeter is in version 5 of Brainard's UCSB psychophysical toolbox%% After initializing colorimeter, it should say "remote mode"%% on the LCD display. Now we need to issue command strings to the colorimeter%% to retrieve data from files.%% The command strings are documented on page B-17 of the manual.% 01.20.98 ABP -- This is the Newsome lab monitor phosphors.s = cmeter('Init');cmeter('Cmd', 'R121');r = cmeter('Spectrum');         cmeter('Cmd', 'R122');g = cmeter('Spectrum');         cmeter('Cmd', 'R123');b = cmeter('Spectrum');         cmeter('Cmd', 'R124');w = cmeter('Spectrum');         save newsomeRaw r b g w